{{DISPLAYTITLE:VDW_RADIUS}}
{{TAGDEF|VDW_RADIUS|[real]|50}}

Description: Defines the cutoff radius (in <math>\AA</math>) for the van der Waals pair interactions.
----

{{TAG|VDW_RADIUS}} sets the cutoff radius for the van der Waals pair interactions in <math>\AA</math> for the [[DFT-D2]], [[DFT-D3]], [[DFT-ulg]], [[DDsC_dispersion_correction|DDsC]], and [[Tkatchenko-Scheffler_method|Tkatchenko-Scheffler]] methods.

